35:47.613 --> 35:49.381
I thought it over,
and I realized

35:49.481 --> 35:52.351
I wasn't being very
responsible.

35:52.451 --> 35:54.186
I should have at least told you
where I was going.

35:54.286 --> 35:55.554
TAS: She's up there.

35:55.654 --> 35:58.023
I'm in Oakland.

35:58.123 --> 36:01.227
I'm staying at this house
on Argyle Street, 4051.

36:01.327 --> 36:03.229
(indistinct conversations)

36:03.329 --> 36:06.265
I'm using someone else's phone,
so don't bother calling back,

36:06.365 --> 36:08.066
but I just thought you should
know where I am

36:08.166 --> 36:09.901
in case of an emergency.

36:10.001 --> 36:15.006
**

36:15.106 --> 36:20.178
**

36:20.279 --> 36:25.284
**

36:25.384 --> 36:27.185
CHANCE: Hey.

36:27.286 --> 36:30.055
Nic, I swear to you
I had nothing to do

36:30.155 --> 36:33.191
