to send you to that camp.

36:33.292 --> 36:35.427
Your mom -- She didn't
tell me about it

36:35.527 --> 36:36.862
until after she'd done it.

36:36.962 --> 36:39.598
And I drove out there. I was --
I was gonna come get you,

36:39.698 --> 36:43.535
and I --
(sighs) I got arrested.

36:43.635 --> 36:44.870
What?

36:44.970 --> 36:47.939
I -- I beat someone up.

36:48.039 --> 36:50.208
(sighs)

36:50.309 --> 36:52.077
Oh, babe.

36:52.177 --> 36:54.813
Oh, God,
it's good to see you.

36:54.913 --> 36:56.081
How're you doing?

36:56.181 --> 36:57.716
I'm okay.

36:57.816 --> 37:00.252
Listen, Nic,
I am going to plead guilty.

37:00.352 --> 37:01.953
Why?

37:02.053 --> 37:03.589
Because I am.

37:03.689 --> 37:07.326
Because I did it,
and I needed to stop.

37:07.426 --> 37:08.994
Yeah, but,
so you go to prison?

37:09.094 --> 37:10.128
Uh-huh.

37:10.228 --> 37:11.430
For how long?

37:11.530 --> 37:14.232
I don't know.
Could be two years.

37:15.434 --> 37:17.336
It could be less.
It could be less!

37:17.436 --> 37:20.939
Hey, listen, Nic,
you're -- two years.

37:22.173 --> 37:24.410
Two years,
you're going to be eighteen.

37:24.510 --> 37:26.312
All right, you're going to be
starting out

37:26.412 --> 37:27.913
on a whole,
new stage of life.

37:28.747 --> 37:32.117
Maybe we can take that step
together.

37:32.217 --> 37:34.786
(voice breaking) Yeah, but
what happens until then?

37:34.886 --> 37:36.588
(sighs)

37:36.688 --> 37:38.123
Dad, no.

37:38.223 --> 37:40.191
Dad, no, I-I can't live
with her, you know that!

37:40.292 --> 37:42.961
Yeah, I know.
Listen, listen.

37:44.996 --> 37:48.334
Look, I know you're --
I know you're angry.

37:48.434 --> 37:49.868
(sighs)

37:49.968 --> 37:54.540
But people fuck up,
all right?

37:54.640 --> 37:57.343
It's the -- it's the
distinguishing characteristic

37:57.443 --> 37:59.711
of our species.

38:01.513 --> 38:05.283
And bad decisions,
they can come from malice

38:05.384 --> 38:08.787
or sometimes love,
but if you think hard,

38:08.887 --> 38:12.558
you know deep down what side of
the line your mother lives on.

38:12.658 --> 38:16.061
**

38:16.161 --> 38:17.629
(sniffles)

38:17.729 --> 38:20.966
And I know that you're not
the only one who feels lost.

38:21.066 --> 38:22.968
Dad, I can't!

38:23.068 --> 38:26.004
I can't just go back to her
like it didn't happen!

38:26.104 --> 38:27.639
Honey,
you can't stay here.

38:27.739 --> 38:29.341
Well, I-I could stay
with Carl and D.

38:29.441 --> 38:32.310
No, baby. Carl's with his
family. D's in Tijuana.

38:32.411 --> 38:34.513
Well, then, here.

38:34.613 --> 38:36.582
Dad, you're going
to prison.

38:36.682 --> 38:38.417
Here is the only place.

38:38.517 --> 38:41.820
**

38:41.920 --> 38:43.755
Well, then, where?

38:43.855 --> 38:48.026
**

38:48.126 --> 38:52.263
**

38:52.364 --> 38:56.502
**

38:56.602 --> 39:00.739
**

39:00.839 --> 39:04.943
**

39:05.043 --> 39:07.579
Thank you, Lucy.
It means a lot

39:07.679 --> 39:08.947
just knowing she's here
with you

39:09.047 --> 39:11.016
until she figures
stuff out with her mother.

39:11.116 --> 39:13.619
I-I can't tell you --
-You don't have to. I get it.

39:13.719 --> 39:16.121
I mean, hmm,
I don't -- I don't get it,

39:16.221 --> 39:18.724
but I assume that I will
one day

39:18.824 --> 39:22.794
and, in the meantime,
actual free babysitting.

39:25.564 --> 39:27.365
I got something for you.

39:27.466 --> 39:29.701
(trunk opens)

39:32.070 --> 39:33.204
What?

39:33.304 --> 39:34.873
Now, if you want
to sell this,

39:34.973 --> 39:36.908
I would ask for 8 grand
to start with.

39:37.008 --> 39:40.245
If you want to keep it,
I bet it will appreciate.

39:40.345 --> 39:42.280
It's a painting
I bought with Nicole.

39:42.380 --> 39:43.782
It used to hang
in my living room.

39:43.882 --> 39:45.617
It just makes me happy,
I don't know why.

39:45.717 --> 39:48.219
You should keep it.

39:48.319 --> 39:50.255
I don't think they're
gonna let me decorate.

39:50.355 --> 39:53.625
Oh, um, yeah, okay.

39:53.725 --> 39:55.293
Uh, thank you.

39:57.162 --> 40:00.432
Listen, I-I understand
how your parents feel,

40:00.532 --> 40:02.100
but I think
they're wrong.

40:02.200 --> 40:05.270
Besides the occasional
lapse in judgment,

40:05.370 --> 40:07.439
I think you could
really help people.

40:07.539 --> 40:09.608
And you deserve that.

40:09.708 --> 40:10.942
I think you should
go back to school,

40:11.042 --> 40:12.511
you should get your degree,
and get out there,

40:12.611 --> 40:15.914
and you can be for patients
what you've always been for me.

40:16.014 --> 40:18.016
Yeah. Okay. I will.

40:19.985 --> 40:21.352
Good.

40:21.453 --> 40:23.755
**

40:23.855 --> 40:25.256
Anyway...

40:25.356 --> 40:27.826
**

40:27.926 --> 40:31.863
And I want you to figure out
how to be in the world

40:31.963 --> 40:34.199
in a way
that doesn't hurt you.

40:34.299 --> 40:36.802
You deserve that.

40:36.902 --> 40:40.872
**

40:40.972 --> 40:44.943
**

40:45.043 --> 40:46.845
JUDGE MATHEWS:
Dr. Chance, to the charge

40:46.945 --> 40:48.780
of aggravated battery,
how do you plead?

40:48.880 --> 40:52.150
Guilty or not guilty?
-Guilty.

40:52.250 --> 40:54.853
By entering a plea of guilty,
you'll be giving up your right

40:54.953 --> 40:56.555
to have a trial,
do you understand?

40:56.655 --> 40:57.823
I do.

40:57.923 --> 40:59.457
Accordingly,
I find the defendant

40:59.558 --> 41:01.226
is acting voluntarily

41:01.326 --> 41:03.228
and that he fully understands
his rights.

41:03.328 --> 41:05.497
Therefore, I accept
the plea of guilty

41:05.597 --> 41:07.298
to the charge
of aggravated battery

41:07.398 --> 41:11.069
as outlined
in docket number 401217.

41:11.169 --> 41:14.239
I see the state has submitted
their sentencing recommendation?

41:14.339 --> 41:16.307
Yes, Your Honor.

41:16.407 --> 41:18.143
Given the violent nature
of this crime

41:18.243 --> 41:21.146
and the serious injuries
Mr. Pitt sustained,

41:21.246 --> 41:24.182
we ask the court for the maximum
sentence of four years.

41:24.282 --> 41:26.417
I understand that both parties
want to present witnesses

41:26.518 --> 41:28.754
to help with my sentencing
recommendation.

41:28.854 --> 41:31.189
Mr. Jakes, I have your list
of names here.

41:31.289 --> 41:32.658
Yes, Your Honor.

41:32.758 --> 41:35.026
And the prosecution would
like to present someone,

41:35.126 --> 41:36.728
Ms. Saavedra?
-Yes, Your Honor.

41:36.828 --> 41:39.565
I expect Dr. Clayton
to be here shortly.

41:39.665 --> 41:42.534
