and think,

41:47.038 --> 41:49.040
"I'm going to become
a fucking vigilante"?

41:50.842 --> 41:52.778
Mr. Jakes,
are you ready to proceed?

41:52.878 --> 41:53.845
Yes, Your Honor.

41:53.945 --> 41:56.181
