desires, your responses.

49:14.252 --> 49:16.821
**

49:16.921 --> 49:19.390
You're going to be staring
down the barrel

49:19.490 --> 49:20.891
of the rest of your life

49:20.992 --> 49:23.128
without anyone to help you
achieve them.

49:26.564 --> 49:28.833
What a thing it is,
in life,

49:28.933 --> 49:32.703
to find even one person who
understands your darkest heart,

49:32.803 --> 49:34.972
let alone two.

49:35.073 --> 49:36.574
You're right.

49:36.674 --> 49:39.010
He is gone.

49:39.110 --> 49:41.179
But I'm not alone.

49:41.279 --> 49:44.015
I wouldn't do that
to myself.

49:44.115 --> 49:45.316
Come on, doc.

49:45.416 --> 49:48.053
You think I don't know
