that I've learned from my job,

49:52.590 --> 49:54.092
it's how to prepare,

49:54.192 --> 49:57.862
it's how to play
the long game, right?

49:57.962 --> 50:02.333
He is gone,
but I'm not alone.

50:02.433 --> 50:04.902
(echoing)
