JUDGE MATHEWS: Mr. Jakes, have
you heard from your client?

51:15.673 --> 51:18.443
JAKES:
I spoke to him yesterday, at
which point he clearly stated

51:18.543 --> 51:20.010
he would be present
at today's hearing.

51:20.111 --> 51:21.646
Have you spoken
with him today?

51:21.746 --> 51:23.948
I have tried to reach him
repeatedly, Your Honor,

51:24.048 --> 51:26.751
but, as of yet,
I have not been able to.

51:26.851 --> 51:30.755
(indistinct talking)

51:30.855 --> 51:33.424
Then I have no choice but
to suspend my decision,

51:33.524 --> 51:35.126
levy a fine of $10,000,

51:35.226 --> 51:37.962
and issue a bench warrant
for Dr. Chance's arrest.

51:38.062 --> 51:40.431
(gavel bangs)

51:40.531 --> 51:43.368
**

51:43.468 --> 51:45.170
Hey.

51:45.270 --> 51:46.637
Where is he?

51:46.737 --> 51:52.177
**

